# Strict block list — phrases that must never appear anywhere in the working
# tree, regardless of path. Copy to .publish-guard-strict.local (gitignored)
# and edit. Scanned by scripts/publish-guard-strict-scan.sh on every commit,
# push, and smoke-test. Block on hit, no exemptions.
#
# ERE regex, one per line. Blank lines and #-comments ignored.
#
# This list is the "always-block" tier: phrases that should not appear in
# private retros, archive prompts, HANDOFF/RUNBOOK, or anywhere else. For
# path-dependent patterns (machine paths, persona names) use .publish-guard.local
# which honours an exemption list for private-tier paths.

\bCV\b
curriculum vitae
recruiter
hiring manager
cover letter
job.search
interview prep
\bIR35\b
day rate
interim CTO
fractional CTO
